front.title: •A Trophy Sacrificed
front.gametext: To play this Interrupt, you must first place a card stacked on Jabba's Trophies in owner's Lost Pile. USED: Draw top card of Reserve Deck.  LOST: Cancel an attempt to use a weapon to target your alien. OR Cancel Sense.
front.lore: Jabba's minions could be expected to be sacrificed to save the Hutt, to destroy one of the Hutts enemies or to provide the Hutt and his minions with a good laugh.
